Title: Himalaya Nourishing Skin Cream(250 ml)
Description: Nourishing Skin Cream: For skin that's nourished. What it does: Himalaya’s Nourishing Skin Cream is a light, nongreasy, daily-use cream, which provides you all day moisturizing, nourishment and protection. The cream is blended with the extracts of Aloe Vera, Winter Cherry, Indian Kino Tree and Indian Pennywort, which protect your skin from pollution and dry weather and provide nourishment and moisture. Key ingredients: Aloe Vera, known for its many healing properties, can be used topically or consumed in its juice form. The leaf of this plant has a number of therapeutic properties. It is rich in enzymes, polysaccharides and nutrients which exhibit antibacterial and antifungal action. A natural UV inhibitor, its hydrating, softening and intense moisturizing properties nourish the skin. Winter Cherry is an effective anti-stress agent that has a mild tranquilizing action. In skincare, this plant is used for its antioxidant properties, which help skin cell regeneration. Indian Kino Tree grows in the hilly regions of India. Its astringent properties work as a skin tonic to tone and rejuvenate facial skin. Indian Pennywort is regarded as the best home remedy for skin disorders such as chronic ulcers and persistent eczema.

Title: Protein Kera Cysteine Hair Styler
Description: Protein Kera Cysteine Treatment is completely free of formaldehyde producing ingredients. Cysteine is one of the many amino acids that combine to form keratin, allowing for powerful moisture retention. Cysteine Protein blend, which reacts with hydrogen and oxygen, causing the molecules to attach themselves to each other and filling protein in the gaps of the hair shaft. This is what eliminates the frizz, while adding weight to the hair shaft causing the smoother, straighter effect. It helps in repairing dry, damage and frizzy hair. The process of the Protein Kera Cysteine Treatment is very simple. Your Salon provider will first wash your hair with the Protein Kera Clarifying Shampoo in preparation for the treatment. Then your hair is blast dried free style until 100% dry with medium heat. Your hair is sectioned to apply the treatment with a brush as you would apply hair color. The treatment is left in the hair for aprox 20-30 minutes. The hair is then blast dried using medium heat to completly dry the product. Finally the hair is flat ironed using very small sections making your hair very smooth, silky, and shiny. It is as simple as 1 - 2 - 3. It is Ideal for Unisex

Title: Enem Acne Pimple Remover LED Light & Heat Therapy Portable Electrotherapy Device
Description: "Enem Acne, Pimple, Blemish Clearing Device is your key to stopping blemishes before they erupt and bloom. You don't have to live with pimples for days if you treat them when they first appear usin this deviceTechnologyAcne light therapy is the pain-free, low-cost way to get rid of blemishes on acne-prone skin.The device has 3 light treatments:Blue Light: Blue light activate light-sensitive chemicals-porphyrins-found in the outer cell membranes of the bacteria causing acne. When these vibrate, they rupture the outer lining of the bacterium and it dies within 48 hours.Red Light: Red light reach deeper into the skin, down to the level of the sebocytes that produce the oil that sometimes clogs pores. This helps remove / fade acne spotGreen/Yellow Light: This prevents acne relapse & helps with skin discoloration. USAGE:Before using, examine your skin for signs of blemishes that have not yet emerged such as small, itchy areas or signs of irritation in a specific area; these are indicators of acne that is growing, but not yet fully germinated. Treat such areas with this unit.• Use as needed when you see emerging blemishes.• The earlier you start to treat a germinating spot, the better success you will have.• Select the suitable color treatment by pressing the button and keep near acne• Watch as blemishes treated with this unit shrink or disappear in about 24-48 hours when effectively treated.Tips/DisclaimerThis product is not intended for blackheads or whiteheads and does not address these problems.The Acne Clearing Device is designed for acne in its first day or two; applying this treatment to blemishes older than that is not that effective.Do NOT over use the devicePeople with sensitive skin/severe acne, consult dermatologist before using the deviceBatteries not included"
